name: Ekitipoi
tagline: Various Points of Interest in Ekiti State
body:
### Ekiti Points of Interest
These Points of Interest were collected between January and March, 2011 by the Data Team of DSI during the One Hundred Days Free Health Mission of the Fayemi Administration in Ekiti State, Nigeria.
